      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:3:11:5",
      "text": [
        " سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ الْمُكَاتَبِ قَالَ يَجُوزُ عَلَيْهِ مَا شَرَطْتَ عَلَيْهِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Al Husayn Bin Muhammad, from Moala Bin Muhamammad, from Al Hassan Bin Ali, from Aban, from the one who informed him, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup>, said, ‘I asked him<sup>asws</sup> about the contracted slave. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘It is allowed upon him whatever is stipulated upon him’."
        ]
